 Sourav best choice: Sehwag

New Delhi: Sourav Gangulys reappointment as Team India skipper was welcomed by Virender Sehwag on Saturday. 

I think he is the best choice, Sehwag said at a press conference here to announce the launch of his food court ? Sehwags favourites. 

I think what the selectors have decided is based on past performance and while taking into account what is best for the team, Sehwag said. Ganguly has been the most successful skipper for India, that speaks for his leadership. 

